p%3EEtienne%20De%20Malglaive%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20we%20are%20not%20doing%20anything%20new.%20We%20are%20doing%20the%20same%20business%20model%20that%20has%20been%20operating%20here%20in%20Iceland%20for%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20J%C3%B3nsson%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20just%20knew%20that%20if%20we%20could%20do%20this%20with%20a%20lower%20cost%20and%20offer%20lower%20fares%2C%20we%20would%20be%20successful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20J%C3%B3nsson%20is%20also%20wary%20not%20to%20repeat%20the%20mistakes%20of%20Wow%20Air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20to%20different%20financing%20and%20bad%20business%20moves.%20Wow%20was%20privately%20owned%20by%20one%20person%20whereas%20Play%20is%20listed%20on%20the%20Nasdaq%20stock%20exchange.%20Wow%2C%20the%20extinct%20airline%20increased%20spending%20by%20using%20three%20Airbus%20A330%20jets%20to%20expand%20its%20offerings%20to%20the%20likes%20of%20India%20and%20Los%20Angeles%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0instead%20of%20keeping%20to%20one%20type%20of%20plane%20like%20most%20budget%20airlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlay's%20jets%20are%20all%20part%20of%20Airbus'%20single-aisle%20A320%20family%2C%20and%20J%C3%B3nsson%20said%20it's%20also%20eager%20to%20order%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbus-a321xlr-will-be-a-game-changer-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA321XLR%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20extra-long-range%20version%20of%20the%20A321%20could%20open%20up%20California%20and%20Dubai%20as%20destinations%2C%20without%20the%20need%20to%20retrain%20pilots%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBuilding%20an%20airline%20during%20the%20pandemic%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20advantage%20for%20Play%20is%20that%20it%20has%20the%20youngest%20fleet%20in%20Europe.%20Born%20out%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20it%20was%20able%20to%20start%20on%20a%20more%20even%20footing%20as%20other%20airlines%20suffered%20lower%20demand%2C%20as%20well%20as%20getting%20good%20deals%20on