Fi.insider.com%2F65e9e97a6080194819fd9093%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplay-airline-iceland-cheap-flights-transatlantic-ceo-birgir-jonsson-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Birgir%20J%C3%B3nsson%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Icelandic%20budget%20airline%20Play.%20He%20told%20BI%20how%20Iceland's%20geography%20lends%20itself%20to%20cheap%20flights%20and%20volcanic%20tourism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22psyme%40insider.com%20(Pete%20Syme)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplay-airline-iceland-cheap-flights-transatlantic-ceo-birgir-jonsson-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trinamool's%20'Don't%20Be%20Upset'%20Message%20To%20PMO%3A%20Congress%20On%20Ally's%20Poll%20List%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress%20today%20announced%20candidates%20for%20all%2042%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Bengal%2C%20snubbing%20Congress%20which%20had%20just%20days%20earlier%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bdoors%20are%20still%20open%26quot%3B%20for%20seat-sharing%20talks%20for%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20Trinamool%20are%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20-%20an%20alliance%20of%20opposition%20parties%20that%20had%20come%20together%20to%20challenge%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%20The%20snub%20today%20is%20in%20line%20with%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20declaration%20that%20only%20her%20party%20can%20challenge%20the%20BJP%20in%20Bengal.%20The%20breakdown%20in%20talks%20with%20Congress%20over%20seats%20was%20another%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20hit%20back%20soon%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdefiant-trinamool-fields-mahua-moitra-again-from-krishnanagar-5212403%5C%22%3ETrinamool%20released%20the%20list.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20has%20repeatedly%20declared%20