0you.%20Meanwhile%2C%20you're%20still%20dealing%20with%20the%20financial%20damages%20these%20kids%20caused%20%E2%80%94%20and%20any%20long-term%20impacts%20on%20your%20ability%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score-needed-to-rent-apartment%5C%22%3Erent%20an%20apartment%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20a%20nightmare%20you've%20had%20to%20live%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20help%20you%20find%20your%20way%20forward%2C%20I%20talked%20to%20Ben%20Michael%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fzealousadvocate.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecriminal%20defense%20lawyer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20the%20first%20thing%20you%20should%20do%20is%20try%20to%20settle%20the%20matter%20without%20suing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20encouraged%20you%20to%20explain%20the%20situation%20to%20your%20ex-landlord%20and%20see%20if%20they%20will%20forgive%20any%20debt%20you%20may%20owe%20them%20for%20damages%2C%20broken%20lease%20agreements%2C%20or%20remaining%20rent.%20Maybe%20they'll%20be%20understanding%20maybe%20not%2C%20but%20you%20won't%20know%20until%20you%20try.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3ELearn%20more%20about%20Business%20Insider's%20picks%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-renters-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Ebest%20renters%20insurance%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EConsider%20using%20this%20approach%20with%20the%20young%20woman's%20grandmother%20as%20well.%20Since%20you%20know%20she%20will%20probably%20end%20up%20paying%2C%20try%20to%20figure%20things%20out%20with%20her%20first.%20Be%20honest%20and%20understanding.%20Try%20to%20avoid%20sounding%20accusatory.%20This%20is%20her%20grandaughter's%20fault%2C%20not%20hers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExplain%20how%20her%20granddaughter's%20actions%20financially%20hurt%20you.%20Tell%20her%20that%20while%20you%20would%20rather%20not%20sue%20a%2017-year