0had%20fewer%20sittings%2C%20but%20all%20of%20them%20were%20dissolved%20before%20completing%20the%20full%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20affected%20the%20number%20of%20sittings%3A%20in%202020%2C%20the%20house%20sat%20for%20only%2033%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe.infogram.com%2F897ee810-7c95-48df-ac7b-64881df822d5%3Fsrc%3Dembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22699%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22List%20Of%20Celebrity%20MPs%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22816%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELow%20attendance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECelebrity%20MPs%20had%20an%20attendance%20of%2056.7%25%2C%20on%20average%2C%20our%20analysis%20of%20data%20compiled%20by%20PRS%20Legislative%20Research%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fmptrack%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20lower%20than%20the%20average%20for%20all%20MPs%20(79%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20four%20of%20the%2019%20celebrity%20MPs%20%E2%80%93%20all%20from%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20had%20attendance%20percentages%20above%20the%20national%20average%3A%20Bhojpuri%20actor%20Dinesh%20Lal%20Yadav%20%E2%80%9CNirahua%E2%80%9D%20had%2090%25%20attendance%2C%20Bengali%20actress%20Locket%20Chatterjee%20had%2088%25%2C%20Bhojpuri%20actor%20Manoj%20Tiwari%20had%2085%25%20and%20Olympic%20medalist%20in%20shooting%20and%20a%20retired%20colonel%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army%20Rajyavardhan%20Rathore%20had%2080%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe.infogram.com%2F5f3b3d68-1705-4543-ba8a-5c740ab84fc7%3Fsrc%3Dembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Attendance%20Of%20Celebrity%20MPs%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22713%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBengali%20actor%20Deepak%20(Dev)%20Adhikari%20had%20the%20lowest%20attendance%20(12%25)%2C%20up%20from%2011%25%20in%20the%2016th%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fgovernance%2Fhow-did-celebrity-mps-perform-in-the-17th-lok-sabha-898714%5C%22%3EOther%20names%20on%20the%20list%20with%20low%20attendance%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20Hindi%20actor%20Ajay%20Singh%20Deol%20alias%20Sunny%20Deol%20(17%25)%2C%20Bengali%20actress%20and%20singer%20Mimi%20Chakraborty%20(21%25)%2C%20Bengali%20actress%20Nusrat%20Jahan%20Ruhi%20(39%25)%2C%20singer%20Hans%20Raj%20Hans%20(39%25)%2C%20Hindi%20actress%20Kirron%20Kher%20(47%25)%20and%20actress%20Hema%20Malini%20(50%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFormer%20India%20cricketer%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20logged%2061%25%20attendance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELittle%20participation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOverall%2C%20celebrity%20MPs%20participated%20in%20few%20debates%20and%20discussions.%20Odia%20actor%20Anubhav%20Mohanty%20participated%20in%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20debates%20among%20the%20celebrity%20MPs%20(82)%2C%20followed%20by%20Bhojpuri%20actor-singer%20Ravi%20Kishan%20(81).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHindi%20actors%20Deol%20and%20Sinha%20did%20not%20participate%20in%20any%20debates.%20Adhikari%20participated%20in%20one%20debate%2C%20and%20Gambhir%20and%20Hans%20took%20part%20in%20three%20and%20four%20debates%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fe.infogram.com%2F0cabce31-f833-47d0-9af9-202a9b14d0b2%3Fsrc%3Dembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Debate%20Partcipation%20By%20Celebrity%20MPs%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22713%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFew%20questions%20asked%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20average%2C%20MPs%20in%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20asked%20210%20questions%20each.%20Of%20the%2019%20celebrity%20MPs%2C%20only%20four%20asked%20as%20many%20or%20more%