w%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Karun%20Nair%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1708-karun-nair-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKarun%20Nair%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20first%20slip%20and%20the%20fielder%20made%20no%20mistake%20in%20completing%20the%20catch%20and%20piled%20on%20Iyer's%20misery.%20The%20India%20batter%20has%20not%20performed%20well%20in%20the%20two%20Ranji%20matches%20since%20BCCI's%20central%20contract%20snub.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier.%20India%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20shared%20a%20message%20for%20out-of-favour%20batters%C2%A0Shreyas%C2%A0Iyer%C2%A0and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kishan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107047-ishan-kishan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20need%20to%20get%20fit%2C%20play%20and%20force%20selectors%20to%20'pick%20them%20again'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%C2%A0Iyer%C2%A0and%20Jaiswal%20were%20%26quot%3Bnot%20considered%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20BCCI%20annual%20contracts%20in%20this%20round%20of%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20both%20players%20were%20snubbed%20from%20the%20contracts%2C%20BCCI%20Secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20domestic%20cricket%20forms%20and%20stated%20that%20%26quot%3Bnon-participation%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20will%20carry%20severe%20implications.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishan%20has%20yet%20to%20feature%20for%20India%20in%20any%20format%20since%20opting%20out%20of%20the%20South%20Africa%20series%20last%20year.%C2%A0Shreyas%C2%A0was%20selected%20for%20the%20first%20two%20tests%20but%20got%20dropped%20for%20the%20remaining%20three%20matches.%20He%20opted%20out%20of%20Mumbai's%20Ranji%20Trophy%20quarter-final%20clash%20against%20Baroda%20due%20to%20back%20spasms%20and%20failed%20to%20make%20an%20impression%20in%20the%20semi-final%20against%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20always%20in%20the%20mix.%20Everyone%20who's%20playing%20domestic%20cricket%20is%20in%20the%20mix.%20Firstly%2C%20I%20don't%20decide%20contracts%2C%20right%3F%20Contracts%20are%20decided%20by%20the%20selectors%20and%20the%20board.%20I%20don't%20even%20know%20what%20the%20criteria%20are.%20I'm%20involved%20in%20-%20people%20ask%20me%20my%20opinion%20on%20the%2015%2C%20and%20me%20and%20Rohit%20select%20the%20XI.%20That's%20how%20it%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20Dravid%20said%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference%20after%20India's%20victory%20in%20the%20fifth%20Test%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20never%20discussed%20whether%20somebody%20has%20a%20contract%20or%20not%2C%20whether%20he's%20going%20to%20be%20selected%20in%20the%2015.%20There%20are%20enough%20examples%20of%20people%20playing%20different%20formats%20of%20the%20game%2C%20whether%20they%20have%20contracts%20or%20not.%20I%20don't%20even%20know%20sometimes%20what%20the%20list%20of%20the%20contracted%20players%20is%2C%20when%20we%20take%20these%20decisions%2C%20discussions%20on%20the%2015%20or%20the%20playing%2011%20for%20that%20matter.%20No%20one's%20out%20of%20the%20picture%2C%20no%20one's%20out%20of%20the%20mix%2C%20it's%20just%20a%20question%20of%20hopefully%20them%20getting%20back%20and%20fit%2C%20playing%20cricket%2C%20and%20forcing%20the%20selectors%20to%20pick%20them%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20ANI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710069060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Faqsre6u8_shreyas-iyer_625x300_10_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fshreyas-iyers-poor-ranji-trophy-form-continues-loses-wicket-cheaply-to-ex-kkr-teammate-5212091%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shreyas%20Iyer's%20dismal%20form%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20continued%20as%20he%20was%20dismissed%2