0you're%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20electric%2C%20it's%20completely%20silent%20when%20idling%20(I'm%20not%20too%20well%20versed%20in%20EVs%20I%20admit)%2C%20but%20makes%20a%20whirring%20sound%20not%20that%20far%20removed%20from%20a%20lawnmower%20when%20in%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWheely%20good...%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ami%20steering%20wheel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e79fc090413ab8e1d98ca9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20view%20of%20the%20cabin%20and%20windshield%20from%20behind%20the%20steering%20wheel.%20No%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20the%20red%20button%20does%20either.%20I%20worked%20out%20how%20to%20turn%20on%20the%20(single)%20wiper%2C%20but%20failed%20to%20master%20opening%20the%20%26quot%3Bwindows%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20the%20glass%20roof%20means%20the%20cabin%20gets%20surprisingly%20warm%20inside%20even%20on%20a%20winter's%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlastic%20is%20the%20overarching%20aesthetic%20and%20it's%20the%20flimsiest%20thing%20on%20four%20wheels%20I've%20ever%20driven%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20extremely%20low%20center%20of%20gravity%20does%20give%20some%20sense%20of%20security.%20I'm%20pretty%20sure%20some%20cyclists%20could%20go%20faster%20than%20the%20Ami%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAbsolutely%20no%20bells%2C%20or%20whistles%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Display%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e7abe7ce7f1785b2e6ab14%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20simple%20display%20has%20miles%20per%20hour%2C%20total%20distance%20driven%20and%20the%20level%20of%20charge%20remaining.%20Er%2C%20that's%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBring%20your%20own%20music%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ami%20dashboard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e7a90c90413ab8e1d98e5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ami%20also%20has%20a%20fan%20heater%2C%20hazard%20lights%20and%20a%20USB%20port%2C%20but%20no%20radio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESo%20much%20storage!%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AMi%20dashboard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e7a17ace7f1785b2e6a943%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wide%20dashboard%20has%20all%20sorts%20of%20nooks%20and%20crannies%20for%20storing%20erm%2C%20stuff%2C%20plus%20some%20sort%20of%20holder%20for%20your%20smartphone.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20I%20found%20quite%20difficult%20was%20the%20lack%20of%20an%20interior%20rear-view%20mirror.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20%26quot%3Btrunk%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Luggage%20space%20in%20the%20Ami%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e7a26e6080194819fcdf1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20space%20in%20the%20passenger's%20footwell%20is%20where%20you%20could%20put%20a%20small%20suitcase%2C%20or%20perhaps%20some%20groceries.%20You%20don't%20have%20much%20choice%20as%20there's%20no%20space%20behind%20the%20seats.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cabin%20is%20surprisingly%20roomy%20because%20of%20the%20vehicle's%20height%2C%20and%20without%20a%20passenger%20you%20could%20use%20the%20Ami%20as%20a%20large%20shopping%20trolley.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20bought%20a%20chair!%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C