%20decided%20to%20start%20running%20a%20couple%20of%20supper%20clubs%20in%20my%20spare%20time.%20As%20I%20started%20getting%20back%20into%20my%20passion%20I%20could%20not%20shake%20the%20desire%20to%20have%20my%20own%20premises%2C%20but%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20get%20into%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20some%20friends%20spotted%20a%20competition%20run%20by%20Brixton%20Village%20in%20south%20London%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0they%20were%20offering%20the%20winner%20a%20three-month%20pop-up%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20convinced%20me%20to%20enter%20and%20to%20my%20amazement%2C%20I%20won!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEarly%20days%20in%20Brixton%20Village%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chishuru.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChishuru%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn't%20actually%20open%20until%20September%202020%20because%20Covid%20got%20in%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20soon%20after%20opening%2C%20the%20well-known%20food%20critic%20Jay%20Rayner%20of%20The%20Observer%20newspaper%20came%20in%20and%20kindly%20gave%20us%20a%20rave%20review.%20Brixton%20Village%20then%20asked%20me%20to%20make%20the%20popup%20permanent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20ways%2C%20the%20Brixton%20restaurant%20was%20straightforward%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20a%20small%20site%20with%20just%2018%20covers%20inside%20and%2014%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkeys-to-running-a-profitable-small-business-from-successful-entrepreneurs-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunning%20a%20small%20independent%20restaurant%3C%2Fa%3E%20means%20you%20have%20to%20become%20an%20expert%20in%20everything%20from%20grease%20traps%20to%20licensing%20to%20supplier%20management.%20I%20did%20everything%20myself%20at%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20challenges%20came%2C%20ironically%2C%20with%20the%20reviews%20and%20recognition%20we%20were%20lucky%20enough%20to%20get%20%E2%80%94%20customers%20were%20arriving%20with%20sky-high%20expectations%20that%20we%20struggled%20to%20meet%20in%20a%20tiny%20site%20with%20wobbly%20tables%20and%20no%20toilets%20of%20our%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20took%20on%20a%20general%20manager%20to%20run%20front-of-house%20and%20asked%20my%20friend%20Matt%20Paice%20to%20be%20my%20business%20partner%20in%20May%202021.%20He%20helped%20with%20everything%20from%20day-to-day%20operations%20to%20finance%20to%20strategy%20to%20wine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226360%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Matt%20Paice%20and%20Adejok%C3%A9%20Bakare%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e9b3636080194819fd7020%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224240%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJok%C3%A9%20Bakare%20and%20her%20business%20partner%20and%20co-owner%20Matt%20Paice.%3Cp%3EHarriet%20Langford%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20restaurant's%20success%20continued%20and%20in%20April%202022%2C%20Time%20Out%20named%20Chishuru%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timeout.com%2Flondon%2Fnews%2Fbrixton-markets-chishuru-named-time-outs-best-restaurant-of-2022-041222%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELondon's%20best%20restaurant%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20clear%20we%20had%20outgrown%20the%20site.%20So%2C%20after%20running%20a%20few%20more%20pop-ups%20around%20London%2C%20we%20settled%20on%20our%20Fitzrovia%20space%20in%20central%20London%20last%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMichelin%20visits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20figured%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fguide.michelin.com%2Fgb%2Fen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMichelin%20Guide%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20interested%20in%20us%20in%20the%20Brixton%20days%20because%20they'd%20visited%20anonymously%20and%20then%20tweeted%20some%20photos%20afterwards.%20An%20anonymous%20visit%20happened%20again%20last%20autumn%20at%20the%20new%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226388%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chishuru%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e9c88a90413ab8e1da296b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224259%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChishuru's%20Fitzrovia%20restaurant.%20%3Cp%3EHarriet%20Langford%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20two%20weeks%20before%20the%20ceremony%20an%20invite%20turned%20up%20in%20our%20inboxes.%20We%20thought%20perhaps%20it%20could%20be%20a%20Bib%20Gourmand%20%E2%80%94%20the%20prize%20for%20%26quot%3Bgood%20food%20at%20a%20reasonable%20price.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20they'd%20already%20announced%20that%20list%20a%20week%20before.%20So%20we%20went%20into%20the%20ceremony%20not%20really%20knowing%20why%20we%20were%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20announced%2017%20new%20stars%20for%20restaurants%20across%20the%20UK%20and%20made%20it%20sound%20like%20that%20was%20the%20whole%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20the%20event%20host%20said%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20one%20more%20star%20to%20give%20%E2%80%A6%20it's%20a%20chef%20and%20she's%20cooking%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%20and%20I%20didn't%20hear%20any%20more%20words%20after%20that%20because%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20me.%20I%20was%20stunned%20into%20silence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20weeks%20later%2C%20it%20honestly%20still%20hasn't%20sunk%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatt%2C%20my%20business%20partner%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20I%20would%20be%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblack-female-entrepreneurs-raised-vc-accelerator-customer-acquisition-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20black%20female%3C%2Fa%3E%20Michelin-starred%20chef%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20only%20the%20second%20in%20the%20world.%20That%20really%20resonated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5