indings.%26quot%3BThe%20proliferation%20of%20television%20programmes%2C%20books%2C%20movies%2C%20and%20the%20vast%20amount%20of%20internet%20and%20social%20media%20content%20centred%20on%20UAP-related%20topics%20most%20likely%20has%20influenced%20the%20public%20conversation%20on%20this%20topic%2C%20and%20reinforced%20these%20beliefs%20within%20some%20sections%20of%20the%20population%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20US%20government's%20extensive%20public%20examination%20of%20UFOs%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Bunidentified%20anomalous%20phenomena.%26quot%3B%20Congress%20hearings%20and%20open%20discussions%20with%20NASA%20officials%20have%20been%20part%20of%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20researchers%2C%20there%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bparticularly%20persistent%20narrative%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20government%20has%20secretly%20conducted%20alien%20research%20while%20recovering%20spaceships%20and%20alien%20corpses.%20The%20AARO%20further%20connected%20%26quot%3Bcircular%20reporting%20from%20a%20group%20of%20individuals%20who%20believe%20this%20to%20be%20the%20case%2C%20despite%20the%20lack%20of%20any%20evidence%26quot%3B%20to%20an%20incorrect%20allegation%20that%20the%20government%20is%20withholding%20from%20Congress%20claims%20of%20reverse-engineering%20extraterrestrial%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20%26quot%3Bmisidentification%20of%20never-before-seen%20experimental%20and%20operational%20space%2C%20rocket%2C%20and%20air%20systems%2C%20including%20stealth%20technologies%20and%20the%20proliferation%20of%20drone%20platforms%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20cited%20as%20a%20contributing%20factor%20in%20some%20of%20the%20UFO%20sightings%20claimed%20since%20the%201940s.%20The%20investigation%20said%20that%20the%20AARO%20has%20interviewed%20around%20thirty%20people%2C%20looked%20through%20both%20secret%20and%20unclassified%20records%2C%20and%20reviewed%20all%20government%20UAP%20investigations%20dating%20back%20to%201945.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPentagon%20Press%20Secretary%20Maj.%20Gen.%20Pat%20Ryder%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAARO%20assesses%20that%20all%20of%20the%20named%20and%20described%20alleged%20hidden%20UAP%20reverse-engineering%20programs%20provided%20by%20interviewees%20either%20do%20not%20exist%3B%20are%20misidentified%20authentic%20national%20security%20programs%20that%20are%20not%20related%20to%20extraterrestrial%20technology%20exploitation%3B%20or%20resolve%20to%20a%20disestablished%20program.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDavid%20Grusch%2C%20a%20former%20intelligence%20officer%2C%20stated%20before%20a%20congressional%20committee%20in%202023%20that%20he%20thought%20the%20US%20government%20had%20alien%20bodies%20and%20spacecraft.%20According%20to%20Mr.%20Grusch%2C%20he%20based%20his%20claims%20on%20records%2C%20papers%2C%20and%20discussions%20with%20coworkers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20added%20that%20rather%20than%20attempting%20to%20disprove%20any%20beliefs%2C%20they%20wished%20to%20%26quot%3Buse%20a%20rigorous%20analytic%20and%20scientific%20approach%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20examination%20of%20past%20UAP%20investigations%20conducted%20by%20the%20government%20and%20allegations%20made%20by%20individuals%20who%20said%20that%20the%20government%20and%20contractors%20were%20hiding%20%26quot%3Boff-world%20technology%20and%20biological%20material.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710067680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-03%2Fufo-pixabay_650x400_71520859625.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fufo-sightings-were-misidentification-of-ordinary-objects-pentagon-report-5212093%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Pentagon%20officials%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20public's%20perception%20of%20alien%20visits%20will%20not%20be%20dispelled%20by%20their%20findings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndt