0name%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI'm%20glad%20I%20was%20given%20a%20completely%20different%20name%20from%20my%20twin%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20some%20people%20have%20asked%20why%20our%20parents%20gave%20us%20such%20different%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20they're%20missing%20the%20point%3A%20A%20major%20reason%20I%20love%20my%20name%20is%20because%20it%20sets%20me%20apart%20from%20my%20twin.%20We've%20spent%20our%20lives%20sharing%20things%20%E2%80%94%20why%20should%20a%20name%20be%20one%20of%20them%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20at%20least%20five%20sets%20of%20twins%20in%20our%20high%20school%2C%20and%20they%20all%20had%20similar%20names.%20Their%20names%20either%20rhymed%2C%20began%20with%20the%20same%20letter%2C%20or%20had%20a%20similar%20number%20of%20syllables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20broad%20trend.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goodto.com%2Ffamily%2Ftwin-names-baby-name-ideas-6976%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGood%20To%20Know's%20round-up%20of%20the%20500%20best%20twin%20baby%20names%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023%2C%20names%20like%20%26quot%3BAida%20and%20Ava%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BGabriella%20and%20Isabella%26quot%3B%20topped%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20parents'%20mindsets%20are%20slowly%20shifting%20on%20this%20topic.%20SJ%20Strum%2C%20a%20baby-name%20expert%20based%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20told%20me%20she's%20noticed%20that%20rhyming%20twin%20names%20have%20decreased%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BParents%20value%20that%20their%20twins%20are%20two%20different%20people%20and%20that%20their%20names%20should%20be%20different%20enough%20to%20help%20other%20people%20get%20to%20know%20them%20individually%2C%26quot%3B%20Strum%2C%20who%20founded%20the%20baby-naming%20consultancy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbabynameenvy%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBaby%20Name%20Envy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said.%3