318_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-s-new-regulations-bring-cheer-to-owners-of-vintage-cars-in-india-124031000318_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Key%20Facts%20About%20India's%20%24100%20Billion%20Deal%20With%20European%20Trade%20Group%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20signed%20a%20free%20trade%20pact%20on%20Sunday%20with%20a%20group%20of%20European%20nations%20-%20Switzerland%2C%20Norway%2C%20Iceland%20and%20Liechtenstein%20-%20committing%20to%20reduce%20tariffs%2C%20while%20New%20Delhi%20receives%20%24100%20billion%20in%20investments%20over%20the%20next%2015%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20the%20members%20of%20the%20European%20Free%20Trade%20Association%20(EFTA)%20held%2021%20rounds%20of%20talks%20over%2016%20years%20to%20clinch%20the%20broad-based%20Trade%20and%20Investment%20Agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20key%20facts%20about%20the%20trade%20pact%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBOOST%20TO%20TRADE%2C%20INVESTMENT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20expects%20that%20the%20pact%2C%20following%20deals%20with%20the%20UAE%20and%20Australia%2C%20will%20boost%20exports%20of%20pharmaceuticals%2C%20garments%2C%20chemicals%20and%20machinery%20while%20attracting%20investments%20in%20automobiles%2C%20food%20processing%2C%20railways%20and%20the%20financial%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20the%20EFTA's%20fifth-largest%20trading%20partner%20after%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Britain%20and%20China%2C%20with%20total%20two-way%20trade%20touching%20%2425%20billion%20in%202023%2C%20its%20trade%20ministry%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20exports%20to%20the%20EFTA%20touched%20%242.8%20billion%20and%20imports%20were%20about%20%2422%20billion%20during%20that%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20population%20of%2013%20million%20and%20combined%20GDP%20of%20more%20than%20%241%20trillion%2C%20the%20EFTA%20nations%20are%20the%20world's%20ninth%20largest%20merchandise%20trader%20and%20its%20fifth%20largest%20in%20commercial%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESWISS%20COMPANIES%20TO%20BENEFIT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwiss%20manufacturers%20of%20machinery%2C%20luxury%20items%20such%20as%20watches%20and%20transport%20are%20expected%20to%20benefit%2C%20the%20Swiss%20government%20says.%20India%20has%20invited%20Swiss%20transport%20companies%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20railways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pact%20allows%20EFTA%20nations%20the%20opportunity%20to%20export%20processed%20food%20and%20beverages%2C%20electrical%20machinery%2C%20and%20other%20engineering%20products%20to%20a%20potential%20market%20of%201.4%20billion%20people%20at%20lower%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pharmaceutical%20and%20medical%20devices%20industry%20within%20the%20bloc%20could%20also%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EINDIA-SWISS%20RELATIONS%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20hopes%20the%20pact%20will%20improve%20trade%20ties%20with%20Switzerland%20-%20the%20biggest%20partner%20in%20the%20EFTA.%20India%20is%20its%20fourth-largest%20trading%20partner%20in%20Asia%20and%20the%20largest%20in%20South%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20300%20Swiss%20companies%20such%20as%20Nestle%2C%20Holcim%2C%20Sulzer%2C%20and%20Novartis%2C%20apart%20from%20banks%20such%20as%20UBS%20operate%20in%20India%2C%20while%20Indian%20IT%20majors%20TCS%2C%20Infosys%20and%20HCL%20work%20in%20Switzerland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETOUGH%20NEGOTIATIONS%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20government%20has%20often%20criticised%20predecessor%20governments%20for%20compromising%20the%20interests%20of%20domestic%20industry%20in%20trade%20pacts%20and%20moved%20slowly%20in%20seeking%20a%20firm%20commitment%20to%20increase%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalks%20on%20trade%20pacts%20have%20run%20for%20years%20with%20Britain%2C%20the%20European%20Union%20and%20other%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENO%20TO%20DATA%20EXCLUSIVITY%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20earlier%20rejected%20the%20four%20nations'%20demand%20for%20the%20pact%20to%20include%20provisions%20on%20%26quot%3Bdata%20exclusivity%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20its%20drug%20companies%20to%20produce%20generic%20variants%20of%20the%20off-patent%20drugs%2C%20Indian%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20the%20EFTA%20also%20agreed%20to%20largely%20keep%20%26quot%3Bsensitive%26quot%3B%20farm%20products%20and%20gold%20imports%20out%20of%20the%20pact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELIMITATIONS%20OF%20THE%20PACT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwitzerland's%20policy%20of%20tariff-free%20entry%20for%20all%20industrial%20goods%20from%20any%20country%2C%20with%20effect%20from%20Jan.%201%2C%20would%20affect%20benefits%20to%20Indian%20companies%2C%20Global%20Trade%20Research%20Initiative%2C%20a%20think%20tank%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20says%20in%20a%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20likely%20to%20keep%20facing%20difficulties%20in%20exporting%20farm%20produce%20to%20Switzerland%20due%20to%20a%20complex%20web%20of%20tariffs%2C%20quality%20standards%2C%20and%20approval%20requirements%2C%20analysts%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710067140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fklfgnd9_rupee-generic_625x300_15_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkey-facts-about-indias-100-billion-deal-with-european-trade-group-5211586%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20signed%20a%20free%20trade%20pact%20on%20Sunday%20with%20a%20group%20of%20European%20nations%20-%20Switzerland%2C%20Norway%2C%20Iceland%20and%20Liechtenstein%20-%20committing%20to%20reduce%20