0was%20that%20during%20this%20tumultuous%20period%2C%20Musk%20was%20also%20working%20on%20a%20deal%20to%20take%20over%20OpenAI%2C%20the%20artificial-intelligence%20startup%20that%20created%20ChatGPT%20and%20is%20now%20worth%20%2486%20billion.%20We%20did%20not%20know%20he'd%20suggested%20that%20OpenAI%20raise%20%241%20billion%2C%20merge%20with%20Tesla%2C%20and%20name%20him%20CEO.%20And%20we%20did%20not%20know%20that%20he%20was%20selling%20this%20structure%20to%20OpenAI's%20founders%20as%20their%20company's%20last%2C%20best%2C%20and%20maybe%20only%20hope%20for%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20thanks%20to%20OpenAI's%20present-day%20fight%20with%20Musk%2C%20we%20know%20these%20things.%20And%20it's%20not%20hard%20to%20see%20how%20Musk's%20two%20desires%20%E2%80%94%20saving%20Tesla%20and%20wresting%20control%20of%20Open%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20are%20connected.%20He's%20angry%20at%20OpenAI%20for%20giving%20other%20investors%20the%20opportunity%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20powerful%20company%20he%20wanted%20for%20himself.%20But%20he%20never%20approached%20OpenAI%20and%20its%20founders%20as%20respected%20business%20partners%3B%20he%20approached%20them%20like%20a%20frat%20boy%20who%20puts%20down%20girls%20he's%20interested%20in%20because%20he's%20terrified%20of%20rejection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20overtures%20came%20to%20light%20on%20Tuesday%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-brings-receipts-elon-musk-involvement-openai-lawsuit-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20published%20a%20blog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20detailing%20the%20company's%20relationship%20and%20communications%20with%20Musk%20dating%20back%20to%20its%20formation%20in%202015.%20The%20blog%20post%20was%20a%20response%20to%20Musk's%20decision%20to%20sue%20OpenAI%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20breaching%20its%20contract%20to%20remain%20a%20nonprofit.%20(The%20company%20created%20a%20%26quot%3Bcapped%20profit%26quot%3B%20division%20in%202019%20to%20attract%20investors%20and%20pay%20top-tier%20AI%20talent.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20blog%20post%20and%20emails%20indicate%20that%20in%202015%2C%20Musk%20pushed%20the%20OpenAI%20founders%20Greg%20Brockman%20and%20Sam%20Altman%20to%20raise%20far%20more%20money%20than%20they%20felt%20they%20needed%20to.%20The%20duo%20wanted%20to%20start%20by%20gathering%20%24100%20million%20from%20investors%2C%20but%20Musk%20pushed%20them%20to%20raise%20%241%20billion%20to%20compete%20with%20megacompanies%20like%20Google%20and%20Facebook%20(now%20Meta).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20emails%20also%20indicate%20that%20by%202017%2C%20contrary%20to%20Musk's%20accounts%2C%20the%20Tesla%20CEO%20didn't%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20OpenAI%20becoming%20for-profit%20as%20long%20as%20he%20could%20take%20control%20of%20the%20company.%20In%20February%202018%2C%20Musk%20even%20suggested%20merging%20OpenAI%20with%20Tesla%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20automaker%20could%20be%20OpenAI's%20%26quot%3Bcash%20cow%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20Tesla%20was%20%26quot%3Bthe%20only%20path%20that%20could%20even%20hope%20to%20hold%20a%20candle%20to%20Google.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20extremely%20aggressive%20sell%20to%20Altman%20and%20Brockman%20%E2%80%94%20very%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXTzTkRU6mRY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecome%20with%20me%20if%20you%20want%20to%20live%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20vibes.%20But%20it%20was%20really%20Tesla%20that%20desperately%20needed%20a%20lifeline.%20Musk%20clearly%20saw%20OpenAI's%20potential%20to%20raise%20capital%2C%20and%2C%20coincidentally%2C%20that's%20what%20he%20needed%20right%20then.%20It's%20also%20clear%20he%20saw%20the%20importance%20of%20keeping%20OpenAI's%20technology%20a%20secret%2C%20as%20long%20as%20the%20secret%20was%20in%20his%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2018%20was%20a%20very%20bad%20year%20for%20Tesla%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202018%2C%20while%20Musk%20was%20shooting%20off%20merger%20missives%20to%20OpenAI%2C%20Tesla%