ures%2C%20and%20an%20admission%20from%20Musk%20%E2%80%94%20on%20a%20closed%20call%20with%20select%20reporters%20%E2%80%94%20that%20Tesla%20would%20not%20be%20profitable%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20that%20year.%20That%20spring%2C%20Musk%20claimed%20that%20Tesla%20would%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-robo-taxis-elon-musk-pt-barnum-circus-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1%20million%20robotaxis%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20road%20in%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20the%20Shanghai%20plant%20operational%20by%20the%20end%20of%202019%20gave%20Tesla%20the%20opportunity%20to%20sell%20into%20China's%20booming%20electric-vehicle%20market%20and%20massively%20cut%20costs.%20Thanks%20to%20China%2C%202020%20was%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2021%2F01%2F27%2Fbusiness%2Ftesla-earnings.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20year%20of%20annual%20profit%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Model%203%20chaos%2C%20Musk%20continued%20to%20position%20himself%20as%20OpenAI's%20savior.%20In%20a%20December%202018%20email%2C%20he%20implied%20to%20Altman%20and%20the%20other%20executives%20that%20without%20him%20and%20Tesla%2C%20their%20work%20would%20never%20come%20to%20fruition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20probability%20assessment%20of%20OpenAI%20being%20relevant%20to%20DeepMind%2FGoogle%20without%20a%20dramatic%20change%20in%20execution%20and%20resources%20is%200%25.%20Not%201%25.%20I%20wish%20it%20were%20otherwise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20needs%20billions%20per%20year%20immediately%20or%20forget%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20no%20one%20forgot%20it%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20not%20Musk.%20Now%20he's%20suing%20OpenAI%20because%2C%20contrary%20to%20his%20saber-rattling%2C%20the%20company's%20explosion%20since%20the%20introduction%20of%20ChatGPT%20has%20it%20ascendant%20in%20the%20most%20exciting%20field%20in%20tech%2C%20while%20Tesla%20is%20yet%20again%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20weakness.%20Tesla's%20stock%20went%20on%20a%20glorious%20tear%20from%202019%2C%20after%20the%20Shanghai%20factory%20opening%2C%20through%202023.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20what%20Wall%20Street%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BMagnificent%207%26quot%3B%20tech%20companies%20leading%20the%20rally%20in%20stocks.%20But%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20Tesla%20has%20diverged%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20group.%20China's%20economy%20is%20slowing%2C%20and%20America's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-xi-jinping-crush-tesla-elon-musk-american-ev-industry-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric-vehicle%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20slowed%20as%20well.%20Tesla%20is%20in%20a%20price%20war%20that%20has%20thinned%20margins%2C%20and%20sales%20are%20down.%20In%20a%20conference%20call%20in%20January%20after%20Tesla's%20fourth-quarter%20earnings%20%E2%80%94%20a%20miss%20%E2%80%94%20Musk%20didn't%20seem%20to%20have%20a%20plan%20for%20getting%20through%20this%20period.%20Plus%2C%20he%20still%20has%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20money%20suck%20that%20is%20X.%20So%20now%20Musk%20is%20turning%20back%20to%20OpenAI%2C%20hoping%20the%20latest%20charmless%20offensive%20can%20help%20shore%20up%20his%20empire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20Musk%20positioned%20himself%20as%20a%20white%20knight%20in%202018%2C%20Tesla%20was%20in%20dire%20straits.%20Musk%20was%20willing%20to%20go%20to%20any%20length%20to%20save%20Tesla.%20What's%20a%20little%20bullying%2C%20negging%2C%20smoke%20and%20mirrors%3F%20His%20belief%20that%20he%20alone%20can%20fix%20anything%2C%20combined%20with%20a%20relentless%20desire%20for%20control%2C%20eventually%20turns%20all%20negotiations%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bmy%20way%20or%20the%20highway%26quot%3B%20scenario.%20Perhaps%20that's%20why%20Musk's%20pitches%20to%20OpenAI%20have%20all%20the%20finesse%20of%20a%20flailing%20balloon%20man%20outside%20a%20used-car%20lot%20where%20everything%2C%20absolutely%20everything%2C%20must%20go!%20If%20Musk%20indeed%20believed%20OpenAI%20needed%20him%20or%20Tesla%20to%20succeed%2C%20he%20was%20as%20belligerent%20about%20it%20as%20he%20was%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Flinette-lopez%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3ELinette%20Lopez%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-openai-take-over-save-tesla-chatgpt-sam-altman-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710066121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65eb77216080194819fe4dab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-openai-take-over-save-tesla-chatgpt-sam-altman-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20same%20time%20that%20Elon%20Musk%20was%20trying%20to%20take%20over%20OpenAI%2C%20Tesla%20was%20in%20deep%20trouble.%20It's%20not%20hard%20to%20see%20how%20those%20two%20things%20are%20connected.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22llopez%40insider.com%20(Linette%20Lopez)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A102%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-openai-take-over-save-tesla-chatgpt-sam-altman-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Indians%20for%20Palestine'%20Express%20Solidarity%20With%20Those%20Under%20Siege%20in%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10154424%2FGH_wnfxXsAAMWK-.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EUnder%20the%20umbrella%20of%20%E2%80%98Indians%20for%20Palestine%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20group%20of%20concerned%20citizens%20on%20March%207%20held%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Delhi%20to%20highlight%20the%20voices%20of%20Indian%20workers%20who%20have%20been%20directly%20impacted%20by%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20attacks%20on%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthor%20and%20activist%20Arundhati%20Roy%20sent%20a%20written%20message%20of%20solidarity%20which%20was%20read%20out%20at%20the%20meeting.%20%E2%80%9CRacism%20is%20of%20course%20the%20keystone%20of%20any%20act%20of%20genocide.%20The%20rhetoric%20of%20the%20highest%20officials%20of%20the%20Israeli%20state%20has%2C%20ever%20since%20Israel%20came%20into%20existence%2C%20dehumanised%20Palestinians%20and%20likened%20them%20to%20vermin%20and%20insects%2C%20just%20like%20the%20Nazis%20once%20dehumanised%20Jews.%20It%20is%20as%20though%20that%20evil%20serum%20never%20went%20away%20and%20is%20now%20only%20being%20recirculated.%20The%20%E2%80%9CNever%E2%80%9D%20has%20been%20excised%20from%20that%20powerful%20slogan%20%E2%80%9CNever%20Again%E2%80%9D.%20And%20we%20are%20left%20only%20with%20%E2%80%9CAgain%E2%80%9D%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1064867%2Farundhati-roy-on-gaza-never-again%5C%22%3Eher%20note%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Kumar%20of%20the%20Manesar%20General%20Workers%E2%80%99%20Union%20spoke%20at%20the%20event%2C%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20guarantees%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20its%20own%20workers%20being%20sent%20to%20Israel%20and%20who%20number%20in%20their%20thousands.%20He%20said%20Indian%20workers%20face%20harsh%20conditions%20and%20are%20denied%20their%20rights.%20He%20also%20alleged%20that%20because%20they%20were%20not%20getting%20even%20minimum%20wages%20in%20India%2C%20Indian%20workers%20were%20having%20to%20resort%20to%20go%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaya%20John%2C%20who%20teaches%20at%20Delhi%20University%2C%20laid%20out%20the%20shared%20history%20of%20India%20and%20Palestine%20in%20terms%20of%20their%20experience%20as%20colonised%20people.%20This%20shared%20history%20makes%20it%20incumbent%20on%20the%20working%20people%20of%20India%20to%20defend%20Palestinian%20rights.%20There%20is%20a%20need%20today%20for%20an%20international%20solidarity%20movement%20that%20is%20free%20from%20governmental%20control%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeakers%20also%20criticised%20the%20targeting%20of%20journalists%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20difficulties%20in%20reporting%20from%20there.%20Journalist%20Sujata%20Madhok%20cited%20figures%20from%20the%20Committee%20to%20Protect%20Journalists%20on%20how%2090%20Palestinian%20journalists%20and%20media%20workers%20have%20been%20killed%2C%2016%20injured%2C%204%20missing%20and%2025%20arrested%20by%20Israeli%20forces%20since%20October%207%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArka%20Rajpandit%20of%20the%20Centre%20of%20Indian%20Trade%20Unions%20expressed%20solidarity%20with%20Palestinian%20workers.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20between%202006%20and%202022%2C%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20GDP%20had%20plummeted%20by%2027%25%20and%2C%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20according%20to%20the%20ILO%2C%20prices%20of%20essential%20commodities%20have%20shot%20up%20from%20300%25%20to%20over%202000%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710065789000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10154424%2FGH_wnfxXsAAMWK-.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findians-for-palestine-express-solidarity-with-those-under-siege-in-gaza%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Speakers%20also%20criticised%20the%20targeting%20of%20journalists%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20difficulties%20in%20reporting%20from%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findians-for-palestine-express-solidarity-with-those-under-siege-in-gaza%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rahul%20Gandhi%20slams%20'hidden%20intentions'%20of%20'Sangh%20Parivar'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710065706000%2C