petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20challenging%20Mr%20Goel's%20appointment%2C%20arguing%20that%20it%20was%20arbitrary%20and%20undermined%20the%20institutional%20integrity%20and%20independence%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India.%20ADR%20contended%20that%20Mr%20Goel's%20foresight%20in%20seeking%20voluntary%20retirement%20ahead%20of%20his%20appointment%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20entire%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20speed%20of%20his%20appointment.%20The%20bench%20questioned%20the%20%26quot%3Btearing%20hurry%26quot%3B%20with%20which%20the%20Minister%20of%20Law%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20recommended%20Mr%20Goel's%20name%2C%20emphasizing%20the%20need%20for%20a%20transparent%20and%20deliberate%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20August%202023%2C%20the%20court%20dismissed%20the%20petition%2C%20stating%20that%20a%20Constitution%20bench%20had%20previously%20deliberated%20on%20the%20issue%20and%20decided%20against%20cancelling%20the%20appointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20was%20expected%20to%20announce%20the%20date%20for%20the%202024%20general%20elections%20before%20March%2013%2C%20but%20sources%20say%20that%20Mr%20Goel's%20exit%20might%20delay%20the%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710062160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fq3r8129g_rajiv-goel_625x300_10_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcontroversial-entry-abrupt-exit-arun-goel-election-commission-stint-5211575%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arun%20Goel%20stirred%20up%20a%20row%20yesterday%20when%20he%20abruptly%20resigned%20from%20the%20Election%20Commission%20just%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20His%20exit%20has%20left%20the%20three-member%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20with%20only%20one%20office-bearer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engageme