eave%20the%20BJP%20if%20it%20continued%20allying%20with%20the%20JJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWest%20Bengal%20MP%20resigns%20from%20BJP%2C%20says%20will%20not%20join%20another%20party%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%2C%20MP%20from%20the%20Jhargram%20constituency%20Kunar%20Hembram%20quit%20the%20BJP%20on%20Friday%20citing%20personal%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20leave%20my%20party%20for%20personal%20reasons.%20It%20is%20not%20like%20%E2%80%A6%20the%20party%20will%20suffer%20a%20loss%20or%20its%20work%20will%20get%20stuck%20if%20I%20move%20away.%20The%20BJP%20is%20a%20national%20party.%20It%20is%20famous%20all%20over%20the%20world.%20So%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20future%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20depend%20on%20an%20individual%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHembram%20also%20said%20he%20did%20not%20have%20plans%20to%20join%20a%20different%20party%20and%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20leave%20politics%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdo%20%5Bhis%5D%20pending%20work%20which%20includes%20social%20activities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%E2%80%99s%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20Sukanta%20Majumdar%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThePrint%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Hembram%20had%20informed%20him%20that%20%E2%80%9Chealth%20is%20not%20good%20and%20he%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20work%20for%20the%20party%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20active%20for%20quite%20some%20time%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20Majumdar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHembram%20won%20the%20Jhargram%20seat%20in%202019%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Felections%2Fjhargram-lok-sabha-election-results%2F%5C%22%3E44.56%25%20of%20the%20vote%20share%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710059803000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10134916%2FPhotoJet.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fharyana-and-west-bengal-bjp-mps-quit-party-former-joins-congress%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Formerly%20an%20IAS%20officer%20and%20presently%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20Brijendra%20Singh%20said%20he%20quit%20the%20BJP%20following%20disagreements%20on%20certain%20political%20issues.%20According%20to%20news%20reports%2C%20his%20father%2C%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Birender%20Singh%2C%20may%20follow%20in%20his%20son's%20footsteps.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fharyana-and-west-bengal-bjp-mps-quit-party-former-joins-congress%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Supreme%20Court%20Tomorrow%2C%20SBI%20Petition%20For%20Time%20To%20Give%20Poll%20Bond%20Info%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20on%20Monday%20hear%20the%20application%20filed%20by%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20seeking%20an%20extension%20till%20June%2030%20to%20disclose%20details%20of%20each%20electoral%20bond%20encashed%20by%20political%20parties%20before%20the%20scheme%20was%20scrapped%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-judge%20Constitution%20bench%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20will%20also%20hear%20a%20separate%20plea%2C%20which%20has%20sought%20initiation%20of%20contempt%20action%20against%20the%20SBI%20alleging%2C%20it%20%26quot%3Bwilfully%20and%20deliberately%26quot%3B%20disobeyed%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20direction%20to%20submit%20details%20of%20the%20contributions%20made%20to%20political%20parties%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20by%20March%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20B%20R%20Gavai%2C%20J%20B%20Pardiwala%2C%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20will%20assemble%20at%2010.30%20am%20to%20hear%20the%20two%20petitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20landmark%20verdict%20delivered%20on%20February%2015%2C%20a%20five-judge%20constitution%20bench%20scrapped%20the%20Centre's%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20that%20allowed%20anonymous%20political%20funding%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B%20and%20ordered%20disclosure%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20the%20donors%2C%20the%20amount%20donated%20by%20them%2C%20and%20the%20recipients%20by%20March%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20subsequently%20directed%20the%20SBI%2C%20the%20authorised%20financial%20institution%20under%20the%20scheme%2C%20to%20submit%20by%20March%206%20the%20details%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20purchased%20from%20April%2012%2C%202019%20till%20date%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20which%20was%20asked%20to%20publish%20the%20information%20on%20its%20official%20website%20by%20March%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%204%2C%20the%20SBI%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20an%20extension%20till%20June%2030%20to%20disclose%20the%20details%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20encashed%20by%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SBI%20contended%20that%20retrieval%20of%20information%20from%20%26quot%3Beach%20silo%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20procedure%20of%20matching%20the%20information%20of%20one%20silo%20to%20that%20of%20the%20other%20would%20be%20a%20time-consuming%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20application%20said%20due%20to%20stringent%20measures%20undertaken%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20donors%20was%20kept%20anonymous%2C%20%26quot%3Bdecoding%26quot%3B%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20and%20matching%20the%20donors%20to%20the%20donations%20would%20be%20a%20complex%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20submitted%20that%20the%20data%20related%20to%20the%20issuance%20of%20the%20bond%20and%20the%20data%20related%20to%20the%20redemption%20of%20the%20bond%20was%20kept%20recorded%20in%20two%20different%20silos.%20No%20central%20database%20was%20maintained.%20This%20was%20done%20to%20ensure%20that%20donors'%20anonymity%20would%20be%20protected%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20submitted%20that%20donor%20details%20were%20kept%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%20at%20the%20designated%20branches%20and%20all%20such%20sealed%20covers%20were%20deposited%20in%20the%20main%20branch%20of%20the%20applicant%20bank%2C%20which%20is%20located%20in%20Mumbai%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20a%20separate%20petition%20was%20filed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20initiation%20of%20contempt%20proceedings%20against%20the%20SBI%20for%20alleged%20disobedience%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20directives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contempt%20plea%2C%20filed%20by%20NGOs%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20and%20Common%20Cause%2C%20claimed%20SBI's%20application%20seeking%20extension%20of%20time%20has%20been%20deliberately%20filed%20at%20the%20last%20moment%20to%20ensure%20that%20details%20of%20donor%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20donations%20are%20not%20disclosed%20to%20the%20public%20before%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20submitted%20that%20the%20said%20application%20is%20mala%20fide%20and%20demonstrates%20a%20wilful%20and%20deliberate%20disobedience%20%26amp%3B%20defiance%20of%20the%20judgement%20passed%20by%20the%20constitution%20bench%20of%20this%20court.%20It%20is%20further%20a%20clear%20attempt%20to%20undermine%20the%20authority%20of%20this%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20petitioner%20herein%20is%20filing%20the%20instant%20petition%20seeking%20initiation%20of%20contempt%20proceedings%20against%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20for%20wilfully%20and%20deliberately%20disobeying%20the%20order%20dated%20February%2015%20passed%20by%20this%20court%20...%20wherein%20this%20court%20directed%20SBI%20to%20submit%20details%20of%20contribution%20made%20to%20the%20political%20parties%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20by%20March%206%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20contempt%20plea%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20as%20per%20clause%207%20of%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%2C%20information%20furnished%20by%20the%20buyer%20can%20be%20disclosed%20when%20demanded%20by%20a%20competent%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20per%20clause%2012%20(4)%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20electoral%20bonds%20have%20to%20be%20encashed%20within%20fifteen%20days%20failing%20which%20the%20amount%20of%20bonds%20not%20encashed%20are%20to%20be%20deposited%20by%20the%20bank%20to%20the%20PM%20relief%20Fund.%20Thus%2C%20it%20is%20inconceivable%20that%20SBI%20does%20not%20have%20the%20recorded%20information%20readily%20available%20within%20its%20data%20base%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20said%20electoral%20bonds%20are%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20traceable%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20evident%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20SBI%20maintains%20a%20secret%20number-based%20record%20of%20donors%20who%20buy%20bonds%20and%20the%20political%20parties%20they%20donate%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contempt%20plea%20said%20any%20form%20of%20anonymity%20in%20the%20finances%20of%20political%20parties%20goes%20against%20the%20essence%20of%20participatory%20democracy%20and%20people's%20right%20to%20know%20enshrined%20under%20Article%2019(1)(a)%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20availability%20of%20information%20about%20electoral%20bonds%20will%20give%20voters%20a%20chance%20to%20truly%20inspect%2C%20express%20and%20decide%20their%20choices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710059460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fc1l320oo_supreme-court-ani_625x300_23_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-to-hear-on-monday-sbi