20why%20vote%20for%20BJP%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20in%20its%20budget%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20provide%20Rs%201%2C000%20to%20all%20women%20above%2018%20years%20of%20age%20under%20the%20'Mukhyamantri%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(BJP)%20say%20Kejriwal%20is%20wasting%20the%20money%20by%20giving%20Rs%201%2C000%20to%20every%20women%20in%20the%20city.%20I%20ask%20them%20when%20you%20waived%20off%20big%20loans%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20weren't%20they%20spoilt%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20till%20now%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bfraud%26quot%3B%20was%20being%20committed%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20name%20of%20empowering%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTill%20now%2C%20fraud%20has%20been%20going%20on%20in%20the%20name%20of%20empowerment.%20Till%20now%2C%20they%20used%20to%20praise%20a%20woman%20from%20the%20party%20and%20say%20that%20women%20were%20being%20empowered.%20Now%20I%20will%20put%20a%20thousand%20rupees%20in%20every%20woman's%20purse%20every%20month.%20An%20empty%20purse%20does%20not%20do%20empowerment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710056160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fc3gh0c4g_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_22_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-bjp-aap-delhi-dont-serve-dinner-if-husband-chants-modi-arvind-kejriwal-to-women-voters-5211235%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20yesterday%20urged%20women%20voters%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-bjp-aap-delhi-dont-serve-dinner-if-husband-chants-modi-arvin