20But%20the%20Industrial%20Revolution%20began%20two%20hundred%20years%20prior%20to%20this.%20So%20what%20was%20happening%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%2020th%20Century%20to%20fuel%20such%20a%20rush%20in%20the%20consumption%20of%20energy%20and%20materials%2C%20the%20associated%20pollution%20of%20air%2C%20water%2C%20and%20soil%2C%20and%20a%20dramatic%20acceleration%20in%20the%20extinction%20of%20species%20and%20loss%20of%20biodiversity%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10112214%2F1280px-Anthropocene-GreatAccelerationSocioEconomicTrends-1750-2010.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10112214%2F1280px-Anthropocene-GreatAccelerationSocioEconomicTrends-1750-2010.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10112214%2F1280px-Anthropocene-GreatAccelerationSocioEconomicTrends-1750-2010-300x191.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10112214%2F1280px-Anthropocene-GreatAccelerationSocioEconomicTrends-1750-2010-1024x650.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700957%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22762%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESocioeconomic%20Trends%20of%20the%20Great%20Acceleration%2C%20showing%20the%20rise%20in%20consumption%20from%201750%20to%202010.%20The%20data%20graphically%20displayed%20is%20scaled%20for%20each%20datum%E2%80%99s%202010%20value.%20Source%20data%20is%20from%20the%20International%20Geosphere-Biosphere%20Programme.%20Chart%3A%20Bryanmackinnon%2FCC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%2C%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20is%20petroleum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPetroleum%2C%20or%20oil%2C%20is%20the%20most%20energy-dense%20combustible%20we%20know%20of.%20It%20remains%20a%20liquid%20at%20ordinary%20temperatures%20and%20pressures%3A%20easily%20pumped%2C%20piped%2C%20tanked%2C%20stored%2C%20carried%20to%20wherever%20it%E2%80%99s%20needed%20to%20be%20burned%20on-site%E2%80%94or%20even%20within%20the%20bowels%20of%20a%20small%2C%20moving%20vehicle%E2%80%94none%20of%20which%20coal%20nor%20any%20other%20fuel%20can%20do%20so%20easily%20or%20cheaply.%20The%20Great%20Acceleration%20was%20driven%20by%20the%20advancing%20availability%20of%20petroleum%20to%20power%20internal%20combustion%20engines%2C%20making%20it%20possible%20to%20interlink%20the%20world%20through%20industrial%20shipping%20and%20trucking.%20This%20drew%20more%20of%20the%20world%20into%20the%20booming%20capitalist%20economy%20centred%20in%20the%20West%2C%20especially%20the%20United%20States%2C%20to%20a%20degree%20that%20simply%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20possible%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20century%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fnews%2Fgovernance%2Frich-land-poor-people-what-will-be-the-future-of-generations-growing-up-in-jharkhand-s-coal-belt-89534%5C%22%3Ecoal%20companies%20have%20taken%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DC33Wfhu3BX0%5C%22%3Escorched%20the%20ground%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Jharia%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20turning%20what%20had%20been%20a%20home%20to%20Adivasi%20communities%20into%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUzivaxYf1iM%5C%22%3Euninhabitable%20hellscape%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Many%20of%20those%20who%20thereby%20lost%20their%20lands%20and%20livelihoods%20became%20coal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findia.mongabay.com%2F2019%2F10%2Fthe-burning-coalfields-of-jharia-belch-poison-for-local-residents%2F%5C%22%3Eminers%2C%20who%20today%20remain%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findia.mongabay.com%2F2022%2F05%2Ffear-of-job-loss-and-social-security-run-high-among-jharkhand-mine-workers%2F%5C%22%3Epool%20of%20unsupported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1043473%2Ftheyve-nothing-else-here-the-poor-steal-coal-in-jharkhands-mining-hubs-in-order-to-survive%5C%22%3Eimpoverished%20labourers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20daily%20exposed%20to%20toxic%20levels%20of%20pollution%E2%80%94even%20as%20they%20remain%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiforest.global%2F2020%2F11%2Fjharkhand-contributes-to-32-of-the-countrys-reserves-but-loses-more-than-it-gains-from-coal%2F%5C%22%3Eamong%20the%20most%20underserved%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20electrification%20they%20bring%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%94a%20prime%20example%20of%20how%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgrist.org%2Fbusiness-technology%2Fnone-of-the-worlds-top-industries-would-be-profitable-if-they-paid-for-the-natural-capital-they-use%2F%5C%22%3Ereal%20costs%20are%20absorbed%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20those%20on%20the%20peripheries%2C%20while%20benefits%20accrue%20in%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftbody%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftable%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPetroleum%E2%80%99s%20higher%20energy%20density%20shrank%20the%20space%20needed%20to%20carry%20fuel%20and%20expanded%20cargo%20space.%20It%20made%20possible%20the%20vast%20modern%20fleets%20of%20enormous%20shipping%20vessels%2C%20each%20carrying%20multiple%20trainloads%20of%20goods%20halfway%20around%20the%20world%20in%20a%20just%20a%20few%20weeks.%20Petroleum%20made%20it%20possible%20to%20build%20and%20sell%20billions%20of%20scooters%20and%20cars%20and%20trucks%20that%20could%20ferry%20people%20and%20goods%20to%20any%20remote%20little%20town%20or%20village%20left%20behind%20by%20rail%20networks.%20Petroleum%20paved%20the%20roads%20to%20reach%20there%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20food%20systems%20also%20became%20intimately%20tied%20to%20the%20abundance%20of%20cheap%20oil%2C%20from%20making%20artificial%20pesticides%2C%20and%20herbicides%E2%