3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20sounds%20excited%20at%20the%20feat%2C%20and%20he%20should%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20that%20Bappan%20goes%20on%20to%20narrate%20confirms%20my%20belief%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343534%2Fsparsh-asian-paints-start-foundation-initiative-tactile-art-rajasthan-netraheen-kalyan-sangh-jaipur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducation%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20once%20a%20distant%20dream%20for%20this%20young%20boy.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20nine%20months%20old%2C%20my%20parents%20and%20I%20came%20to%20Gurugram%20from%20West%20Bengal.%20I%20never%20went%20to%20school%20until%20I%20was%20eight%20years%20old%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20narratives%20illustrate%20the%20division%20of%20his%20life%20into%20two%20phases%20%E2%80%94%20early%20childhood%20memories%20characterised%20by%20struggle%2C%20and%20a%20happier%20period%20after%20he%20turned%20eight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20moving%20to%20Gurugram%2C%20Bappan%20started%20attending%20classes%20at%20the%20Nayi%20Disha%20NGO%20%E2%80%94%20started%20in%202014%20by%20Seema%20Seth%20%E2%80%94%20right%20near%20the%20slum%20cluster%20where%20he%20lived%20with%20his%20parents%20in%20Harijan%20Basti%20in%20DLF%20Phase%20V%2C%20Gurugram.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20learnt%20so%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341616%2Fbest-books-on-disability-inclusivity-mental-health-stigma-sign-language-books%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emany%20subjects%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20me%20excitedly.%20%E2%80%9CSeema%20ma%E2%80%99am%20would%20take%20us%20everywhere!%20We%20would%20play%2C%20study%2C%20and%20have%20fun.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20currently%20a%20student%20at%20the%20VIDYA%20NIOS%20in%20Gurugram%2C%20Bappan%20shares%20that%20the%20foundation%20of%20his%20educational%20pursuits%20was%20laid%20at%20Nayi%20D